The package maude-mode is an Emacs mode that allows editing Maude code, and running the Maude interpreter as a subprocess of Emacs similar to inferior-lisp mode.

Some useful links:

* [http://sourceforge.net/projects/maude-mode/ Package web site]
* [http://maude.cs.uiuc.edu/ Maude website]

Enjoy.

----
